{
  "page": "Jon Vance",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Atranta.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/50px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/75px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5d/House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg/100px-House_Vance_of_Atranta.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Maester</span><br />Jon</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nJon Vance</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\">House Vance of Atranta</a></li><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Norbert_Vance\" title=\"Norbert Vance\">Norbert Vance</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jon</b>, born <b>Jon Vance</b>, is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Atranta\" title=\"House Vance of Atranta\">House Vance of Atranta</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>. He is the fifth and youngest son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Norbert_Vance\" title=\"Norbert Vance\">Norbert Vance</a>, his four older brothers are: Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ronald_Vance\" title=\"Ronald Vance\">Ronald</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ellery_Vance\" title=\"Ellery Vance\">Ellery</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hugo_Vance\" title=\"Hugo Vance\">Hugo</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kirth_Vance\" title=\"Kirth Vance\">Kirth</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Vance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div><